These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: coffee, fanta
Job: electrician, photographer
Sport: cycling, surfing
Game: poker, billiard
1. Game:billiard is on the left or right of Sport:surfing##3
2. Beverage:fanta is in an even position##4
3. Job:photographer == Beverage:coffee##1
4. Game:billiard is on the right of Game:poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Job   | photographer     | electrician   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Game     | poker | billiard    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: avocado, cabbage
Movie-Genre: action, documentary
Sport: climbing, basketball
Cigar: bluemaster, tiparillo
1. Sport:basketball is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:action == Cigar:tiparillo##1
3. Food:cabbage is on the right of Movie-Genre:documentary##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Sport           | basketball         | climbing     |
| Cigar     | bluemaster   | tiparillo    |

