.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
House: wooden, farmhouse
Nationality: dutch, egyptian
Birthday: january, november
Sport: climbing, soccer
1. Sport:soccer is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. House:farmhouse == Nationality:dutch##1
4. Birthday:january is on the left of Nationality:egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| House           | farmhouse | wooden    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Birthday           | january         | november    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

